      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "INSTA WORTHY (1)  is a three-year-old gelding who is having his first run for the Sharlee Hoffman barn. Finished off last campaign with a fourth at Murwillumbah 12 weeks ago, and missed a whisker there prior. Hasn't trialled publicly, but looks very well placed. Trickier sorting the rest. SHEZA BARBAROSSA (6) went well here fresh three back and pulled up with an issue at Townsville first-up this preparation. Likely improver who may form the quinella. PERFECT FAWAZ (3) resumes for the same stable with Swaffer engaged. She hasn't been seen at the trials but no surprise if she comes back much better. JOT GIRL (5) will be fitter and is likely to race better with the blinkers on for the first time. Will settle closer in the smaller field. SUPER STEVEN (2) resumed, and the former Victorian may show more this time around.",
